      "title": "Using Sexed Semen in Dairy Heifers: A Beginner's Guide",
      "slug": "sexed-semen-in-dairy-heifers-beginner-guide",
      "summary": "Step-by-step guidance on when and how to use sexed semen in dairy heifers to increase replacement heifer numbers while managing conception risk.",
